<p><a name="Notes_and_references" id="Notes_and_references"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Features_new_to_Windows_Vista&amp;action=edit&amp;section=34" title="Edit section: Notes and references">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes and references</span></h2>
